155
00:13:46.784 --> 00:13:47.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Okay!

156
00:13:51.205 --> 00:13:57.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
