160
00:14:11.100 --> 00:14:12.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sometimes.

161
00:14:12.226 --> 00:14:16.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
